body:
While I feel a bit bad for people still trying to climb, I don&#039;t know why everyone else is so upset about balance abnormalities introduced in this of all patches.
{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}} 
This is the last hurrah for the current rune and mastery system. Things are about to shake to their very foundations, and people are unwilling to laugh off things like big Galio damage when he builds damage (even people done with their climb or who never play ranked).
{{sticker:sg-shisa}} 
I admit that certain things are a bit off at present, but can&#039;t we just play around it and try to be happy? Ardent was finally overnerfed, and hopefully that will happen to shiv soon, but I think people should get what fun they can out of the crazy things that pop up in game and in life.
{{sticker:vlad-salute}}
